  "prompt": "A sleek, ultra-premium AI workspace UI inspired by Apple macOS and iPadOS design language, entirely in Korean. The interface features a bright dark mode with deep black and gray background, soft frosted glass effects, and silver/white typography in San Francisco style. The layout is minimal and spacious with wide gaps between panels. Rounded corner buttons and tabs, subtle drop shadows, and smooth animations are visible. Top tabs in Korean: 대화, 작업, 증거, IDE, 경영. Left panel includes an integrated search bar for local/semantic/web searches with path#Lx-y references. Center main panel features a multi-tab Monaco-style IDE with clean syntax highlighting. Right panel offers annotation tools: pencil, circle, and rectangle. Bottom status bar in Korean displays messages like 저장됨, 포트 8000/3037 연결, 증거 확보. Intuitive shortcut hints shown (e.g., Ctrl+→ for tab switching). Overall a high-resolution (1920x1080) screenshot-style mockup with an elegant, Apple-inspired aesthetic.",
